Take the pot and the trash can.
Stand in front of the fridge.
Stand in front of the fridge. Place the pot on the second level and the trash can on the third level. Close the door. Reports 9 seconds. Open the door. Take the pot and trash can. Close the door.
Place the pot on the shelf on the first level of the cabinet.
